"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-product-recommendations-lifestyle-watch-2024-olympics-soccer-games-online-free-1235067364\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByOscar Hartzog  Soccertournaments are officially underway at the2024 Paris Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"16 nations are competing in the men's tournament, and 12 are facing off in the women's competition.\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The US men's national soccer team -\\u00a0who started as one of the favorites - stuttered in their firstOlympicsgame of the tournament, losing 3-0 to host country France.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.9999286441496237, \"rank\": 7.127742269903409e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}, {\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8054863938086719, \"rank\": 0.24085804143835501, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next, they will face New Zealand in a must-win match if they want to stay in the running.\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 380, \"end\": 391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.6999312523653625, \"rank\": 0.3402318284415115, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain, Argentina, France, and Morocco are also among the teams most likely to take home medals this year.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9962391268453261, \"rank\": 0.002931280208727751, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8683965827583771, \"rank\": 0.06364505026564599, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8054863938086719, \"rank\": 0.24085804143835501, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9809364529579541, \"rank\": 0.01568135809669115, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's US side has seen better success out of the gates, taking down Zambia 3-0.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.9999286441496237, \"rank\": 7.127742269903409e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}, {\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9764257160957449, \"rank\": 0.018348974608609597, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Sunday they take on Germany -\\u00a0one of the favorites in the women's tournament -\\u00a0in a highly-anticipated match.\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are looking to watch Olympics soccer online during the 2024 games, read on.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Below is a quick guide on where tolivestreamOlympics soccer games without cable, including ways to watch Olympics soccer for free.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics soccer matches are being broadcast on USA Network and NBC, and Telemundo in Spanish.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\": 0.9726367869927146, \"rank\": 0.028133022905670987, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}, {\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9995374105349097, \"rank\": 0.0002650891167515913, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telemundo\", \"score\": 0.6664127736250449, \"rank\": 0.5005701684595254, \"text\": \"Telemundo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telemundo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telemundo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans without cable can watch Olympics soccer online usingPeacock, or live TV streaming services likeDirecTV Stream,Hulu + Live TV, fubo, andSling, which carry the channels above.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's a breakdown of your best options:  Peacocktakes the gold medal for Olympics streaming this year, offering livestreams of every soccer game, plus special whip-around coverage if you want to watch other events.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock is also very affordable at just $7.99 a month, although there is no free trial.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock offers both live and on-demand content, including sports like WWE, Golf, and Olympics, and series likeThe OfficeandYellowstone.\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"score\": 0.9999999474803203, \"rank\": 5.200202670991796e-08, \"text\": \"WWE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscriptions start at $7.99 a month.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Soccer fans can also watch Olympics games with live TV streaming services that carry NBC and USA Network.DirecTV Streamis a good pick if you go this route, offering streams of both channels for $79.99 a month.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1812, \"end\": 1815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9995374105349097, \"rank\": 0.0002650891167515913, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1820, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999999999893134, \"rank\": 6.5365754176402055e-12, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, you get afive-day free trialto start.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"DirecTV Stream is one of the most comprehensive live TV streaming services with up to 160+ channels, including local channels, regional sports networks, and all popular national channels.\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 2001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DirecTV_Stream\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DirecTV Stream\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DirecTV_Stream\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DirecTV_Stream\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Packages start at $79.99 a month and all subscriptions start with a five-day free trial.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hulu + Live TVwill also let you watch Olympics soccer online with livestreams of NBC and USA Network.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2346, \"end\": 2349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9995374105349097, \"rank\": 0.0002650891167515913, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\": 0.9726367869927146, \"rank\": 0.028133022905670987, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The service starts with athree-day free trialand then costs $76.99 a month after that.\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hulu + Live TV bundles together Hulu's on-demand library and over 95 live TV channels, including local channels and almost all popular national channels.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscriptions also include ESPN+ and Disney+ at no additional cost.\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hulu + Live TV costs $76.99 a month after a three-day free trial.\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"fubooffers aseven-day free trialand carries both NBC and USA Network for soccer livestreams from the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2795, \"end\": 2798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9995374105349097, \"rank\": 0.0002650891167515913, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2803, \"end\": 2814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\": 0.9726367869927146, \"rank\": 0.028133022905670987, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the free trial, packages start at $79.99 a month.\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"fubo's massive streaming plans carry up to 275+ channels, and you can get even more depending on your location.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Packages start at $79.99 a month, and you get seven days to try the service for free.\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Slingis a more affordable cable streaming option, offering NBC and USA Network livestreams in its Blue package.\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3174, \"end\": 3177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9995374105349097, \"rank\": 0.0002650891167515913, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 3182, \"end\": 3193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\": 0.9726367869927146, \"rank\": 0.028133022905670987, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This plan has 46 channels in total and costs $45 a month (no free trial).\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sling is one of the most affordable live TV streaming services, with packages starting at $40 a month.\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can get up to 46 channels in the Sling Orange + Blue plan, plus more withSling's add-ons.\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Want to watch Olympics soccer for free?\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Try using free trials fromDirecTV Stream,Hulu + Live TV, andfubo.\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3583, \"end\": 3597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hulu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hulu + Live TV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hulu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hulu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All of these trials will get you free Olympics soccer streams while the trial window lasts, as long as you cancel before the trial ends.\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GetDirecTV Stream's five-day free trial here,Hulu + Live TV's trial here, orfubo's seven-day free trial here.\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3790, \"end\": 3804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hulu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hulu + Live TV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hulu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hulu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics soccer tournaments kicked off on July 24 with group stage games, and run through the men's gold medal match on Aug 9 and the women's final on Aug 10.\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 4018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Matches start between 9 a.m.\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET and 3 p.m.\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET.\", \"from\": 4062, \"to\": 4065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's a breakdown of the Olympics soccer schedule for each stage:  Men's Olympics Soccer TournamentGroup Stage: July 24-30Quarterfinals: Aug 2Semifinals: Aug 5Bronze Medal Match: Aug 8Gold Medal Match: Aug 9  Women's Olympics Soccer TournamentGroup Stage: July 25-31Quarterfinals: Aug 3Semifinals: Aug 6Bronze Medal Match: Aug 9Gold Medal Match: Aug 10  We want to hear it.\", \"from\": 4066, \"to\": 4440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send us a tip using our anonymous form.\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rolling Stone is a part of Penske Media Corporation.\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4482, \"end\": 4495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"score\": 0.9999998834000575, \"rank\": 1.1469241064393383e-07, \"text\": \"Rolling Stone\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563